@MishkaRogachev thanks for investigation! Indeed, there are 2 problems:

- chatting with non-contact
- losing mutual contact connection randomly (become Pending instead)

> We used to have a mechanism to get the first 1-1 message from a user as a message in the activity center. Maybe it was removed from designs or maybe we just lost it? @John-44 do you know?

@jrainville no it hasn't been removed from the designs, it's still there.  See the designs below (from the Kuba figma) for how *incoming* contact requests (including the message that arrives with the contact request) should be displayed in the notification centre: 
![2023-03-14 13_38_08-Kuba⎜Desktop – Figma](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/22846356/225018627-32c4e906-bd87-425e-bf8c-8bd52e8b6976.png)
